{"tid":1507002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者請重拾利君雅氣勢插追問10項注意 825警察用槍指你哋","createTime":"2019-08-26T03:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T11:06:53.000Z","uid":221265,"like":155,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"089c2396a7483631247a4f987178d70f7ec7f81e","tid":1507002,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:50:25.000Z","msg":"記者大哥大姐<br />\n<br />\n當日林鄭出嚟畀利君雅狂追問插問，打斷錄音機廢話要求講人話<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強出嚟嗰日，人人化身利君雅，迫到佢哋要中斷政治宣傳式背稿，面對你哋<br />\n<br />\n今日，你哋喺記招謝曬皮，等於對自己對市民殘忍。逆權時代，能力越大責任越大，希望你哋可以再次大團結，重拾當日氣勢，不要俾官警政治宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n[red]<br />\n1.強烈要求加時Q A,以往你哋曾嗌咪爭取減少背稿加長Q A,記者會非宣傳大會，加上佢哋永遠遲大到，加長QA+補時理所當然。<br />\n<br />\n2.永遠不要放過追插問721元朗，荃灣北角刀手，警黑勾結。<br />\n<br />\n3.一定要keep住問曱甴仇恨hate speech ，極有可能係警隊洗腦手段，一定不會是個別事件。以往海外極權政府如盧旺達，緬甸對羅希亞人，多番用「去人化」方法，合理殺人；並用social media散播hate speech,fb老闆曾因而被傳召。<br />\n黨媒provoke 「愛國人士」打斬人，警察hea執法製「煙囱」效應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.824nowtv《經緯線》製作了《獨立調查》，全方位踢爆咗監警會絕對不能取代法定獨立調查委員會，重點之一是指出當日林鄭引2011英國騷亂case之荒謬，請跟進。<br />\n<br />\n4.今集《鏗鏘集》多角度踢爆警察在811爆眼少女，太古行刑式開槍等事件講大話，請跟進。<br />\n<br />\n5.近日記招新聞官明顯勁揀「中新」「新華社」等記者問，大家要集氣控訴蒒選問題及傳媒機構。<br />\n<br />\n6.請記者做足功課，問一些有深度，夠力問題，不要辜負市民期待。<br />\n<br />\n7.記者語氣，表達組織能力都好重要，冇神冇氣細聲1999嘅請對鏡練下。亦要練下追問技巧。<br />\n<br />\n8.新屋嶺及一切捕後還押，用私刑侵人權都要追問。<br />\n<br />\n9.開槍及指向記者相信你哋會問，但如官員，警方再以「不在現場」「冇資料」為由hea答，請直斥其非。<br />\n<br />\n10.我知大家承受好大壓力，不論身心。上司打壓，藍絲抹黑，槍林彈雨。但新聞自由一冇，香港玩完，靠你哋，靠香港人守住！<br />\n［/red]"},{"pid":"07c8fde7b06abb292f1e3560d5c5424021b06991","tid":1507002,"uid":29899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:50:56.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=21860866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5606eb703ffe0691c48f7e8a68e622673c905a5","tid":1507002,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:52:17.000Z","msg":"推到有記者睇到"},{"pid":"15ef3cd0232e616f3d2c60f14a0eb16d006f4280","tid":1507002,"uid":2284